<%
title "Features"
description "Sheethub Features"
keywords %w(features benefits)
%>

<div class="animated-banner">
    <h1 class="sheets-heading">Share and sell your music</h1>
    <h2 class="sheets-subheading">SheetHub is a self-publishing platform and community marketplace for musicians. Just 5% per transaction.</h2>
</div>

<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-6">
        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
                Cool! What does SheetHub give me?
            </h4>
          </div>
            <div class="panel-body">
              <p>SheetHub lets you easily publish, share, and sell your music.</p><p>Your files are securely hosted on SheetHub so you don't need to worry about building a website or storing files anywhere. We help you handle everything from payments, sales, emails, and distribution. You'll also get your very own personal portfolio and subdomain!</p><p> SheetHub handles all the technical complexities behind hosting and selling your sheet music online, so you can focus on pursuing your music.</p>
              <p><%= link_to 'Sign Up', new_user_registration_url %> and get started. Add your work, name a price, and start selling instantly. Want us to help you? Email us at <a href="mailto:support@sheethub.co">support@sheethub.co</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    <div class="col-xs-6">
        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
                Awesome! The price?
            </h4>
          </div>
            <div class="panel-body">
                <p>With SheetHub, you have no setup fees, no monthly fees, no hosting fees, no bandwidth fees to worry about. You have <em>unlimited uploads</em>. Just <strike>15%</strike> <strong>5%</strong> per transaction!</p>
                <p class="bg-success"><em class="fa fa-star"></em> Be part of our public alpha and earn <strong>95%</strong>! For a <strong>$5.00</strong> sale, you'll earn <strong>$4.75</strong>!</p>
                <p>You are paid directly to your PayPal account the moment you make a sale. SheetHub never holds any of your earnings. Get paid instantly on SheetHub.
                </p>
                <p><%= link_to 'Sign Up', new_user_registration_url %> and get started.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-center"><em class="fa fa-arrow-down"></em> Read on for more on what you can do on SheetHub!</p>
    </div>
</div>

